snippet.title: QUETZAL | Demo Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Quetzal is a fast-paced, bullet hell platformer highly focused on reactive gameplay. Embrace the behaviour of the dangers ahead of you to forge your path. You’ll discover a mystical underground world, defeat blood ravenous stone creatures, and survive tortuous obstacles in your quest for answers and meaning.

Join our discord community to get the latest updates: https://discord.gg/MCV3pcKGZh

🎮 Play the Demo & Wishlist Quetzal on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1953670/Quetzal/
